Pick
(
	$(v_Switch_Option_CM_YTD)
       
        ,Count(
{$<
[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'},
[Month ID]={$(v_Max_Month_ID)},
 Year=,
Quarter=,
Month=,
[Salesman Key]={'=(sum({1<[Month ID]={$(v_Max_Month_ID)}, Year=>} [Invoice Amount USD])<> 0)'}>}

{$<

[Month ID]={"<=$(=$(v_Max_Month_ID))"},

[Salesman Key]={'=(sum({1<[Month ID]={"<=$(=$(v_Max_Month_ID))"}, Year={$(v_Max_Year)} >} [Invoice Amount USD])<> 0)'}>}


Distinct [Salesman Key])
         
       
    )
